<text id="02-output-contract" title="Methodologies Summary (Product Manager) Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema draft-07 for the rubric artefact this methodology produces, with valid and invalid examples plus forbidden patterns.</summary>

  <section title="Schema (JSON Schema draft-07)">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/methodologies-summary.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": [
    "task_summary",
    "signals",
    "selected_methodology",
    "rationale"
  ],
  "properties": {
    "task_summary": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 10
    },
    "signals": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": [
        "artifact",
        "horizon",
        "decision_shape"
      ],
      "properties": {
        "artifact": {
          "enum": [
            "spec",
            "roadmap",
            "okr",
            "experiment",
            "readout",
            "pricing-decision",
            "rubric",
            "register",
            "playbook-step",
            "checklist",
            "report",
            "decision-record",
            "other"
          ]
        },
        "horizon": {
          "enum": [
            "this-week",
            "this-sprint",
            "this-quarter",
            "annual"
          ]
        },
        "decision_shape": {
          "enum": [
            "binary",
            "ranked",
            "cascade",
            "framework-pick",
            "report"
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    "selected_methodology": {
      "type": "string",
      "pattern": "^[a-z][a-z0-9-]+$"
    },
    "rationale": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 20
    },
    "fallback_used": {
      "type": "boolean"
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": true
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "task_summary": "Prioritize 9 quarterly bets across 2 squads.",
  "signals": {
    "artifact": "okr",
    "horizon": "this-quarter",
    "decision_shape": "cascade"
  },
  "selected_methodology": "okr-cascade-multi-squad",
  "rationale": "OKR artifact + quarterly horizon + cascade shape uniquely routes to okr-cascade-multi-squad.",
  "fallback_used": false
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "task_summary": "do stuff",
  "signals": {
    "artifact": "thing",
    "horizon": "soon",
    "decision_shape": "vibes"
  },
  "selected_methodology": "DoStuff",
  "rationale": "ok"
}
]]></code>
    <note>task_summary too short; signals enums all invalid; selected_methodology not kebab; rationale too short.</note>
  </example>

  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <list>
      <item>selected_methodology not in kebab-case (slug format).</item>
      <item>signals with missing artifact / horizon / decision_shape (incomplete triage).</item>
      <item>rationale shorter than 20 chars (no real explanation).</item>
      <item>fallback_used=false but selected_methodology='methodologies-summary' (lying about fallback).</item>
      <item>two different routing outputs for the same input signals (non-determinism).</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-methodologies-summary.py">Validator script enforcing this schema</reference>
</text>
